<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
   <title>Survey</title>
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.7.2/css/bulma.css" />
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">

    
</head>

<body>
<div style="width:70%; margin:0 auto; padding:5rem;">
<form id="survey2" class="survey2"  method="post" name="myForm" action="/finalFormSubmit/<%= mainData[0].userID%>">

    <h4>How distracted were you during the tasks? </h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="distraction" name="distraction">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Very focused</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Very Distracted</p>
           
        </div>
    </div>
    <br><br><br>

<h4>Please rate your general emotional state throughout the tasks as being very negative (sad, angry, or highly stressed) or very positive (happy, joyful, pleasant): </h4>
<div class="range">
<input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="emotion" name="emotion">
    <div class="sliderticks">
        <p>Very Negative</p>
        <p>2</p>
        <p>3</p>
        <p>4</p>
        <p>Very Positive</p>
       
    </div>
</div>
<br><br><br>

<div id="musicQuestion">
    <h4>Please rate how the music affected you emotionally.</h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="musicAffect" name="musicAffect">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Very Negatively</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Very Positively</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br><br><br>
</div>



<!--Additional levers and questions-->
<div id="volumeQuestion">
    <h4>How loud did you feel the music was?</h4>            
    <input type="radio" id="volume" name="volume" value="1"> Too quiet<br>
    <input type="radio" id="volume" name="volume" value="2"> Fairly quiet<br>
    <input type="radio" id="volume" name="volume" value="3"> Normal<br>
    <input type="radio" id="volume" name="volume" value="4"> Fairly loud<br>
    <input type="radio" id="volume" name="volume" value="5"> Too Loud<br>
    <br><br><br>
</div>




<div id="enjoyment">
    <h4>How much did you enjoy completing the tasks?</h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="enjoyment" name="enjoyment">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Very little</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Very much</p>
        </div>
    </div>
 
</div>
<br><br><br>

<h4>How much anxiety did you experience while completing the tasks?</h4>            
<div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="anxiety" name="anxiety">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>None</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Extreme Anxiety</p>
        </div>
    </div>

<br><br><br>

<div id="challenge">
    <h4>How challenging did you find the tasks?</h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="challenge" name="challenge">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Not challenging</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Very challenging</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
<br><br><br>

<div id="comfort">
    <h4>How physically comfortable were you during the experiment (tempurature, sitting position, lighting)?</h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="comfort" name="comfort">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Very uncomfortable</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Very comfortable</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
<br><br><br>

<div id="recentExp">
    <h4>Over the past three months, how frequently have you engaged in tasks similar to the ones you just completed for this study?</h4>
    <div class="range">
    <input type="range" step="1" min="1" max="5" value="1" class="slider" id="recentExp" name="recentExp">
        <div class="sliderticks">
            <p>Never</p>
            <p>2</p>
            <p>3</p>
            <p>4</p>
            <p>Daily</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
<br><br><br>




<label>Please indicate your relationship status.</label>
<br>
<label class="labelSpecial">
    <input type="radio" name="maritalStatus" id="maritalStatus" value="relationship"> In a relationship
</label>           

<label class="labelSpecial">
    <input type="radio" name="maritalStatus" id="maritalStatus2" value="not"> Not in a relationship
</label>
<br><br><br>


<label>Please indicate your gender.</label>
<br>
<label for="gender1" class="labelSpecial">
    <input type="radio" name="gender" id="gender1" value="male"> Male
</label>           

<label for="gender2" class="labelSpecial">
    <input type="radio" name="gender" id="gender2" value="female"> Female
</label>
<label for="gender3" class="labelSpecial">
        <input type="radio" name="gender" id="gender3" value="other"> Other
</label>

<br><br>
<br>

<label>Please indicate your education in number of years (including primary and secondary):</label>
<br>
<input type="number" class="col-2 form-control" id="educationLevel" name="educationLevel">
